<p>Most lists of local business listing sites give you 20 directories and call it a day. We went further. This guide covers 100+ local business listing sites, starting with the 25 most impactful directories (with full breakdowns), followed by 75+ more organized by industry and category.</p>
<p>We ranked every site by DA score, cost, link type, and which industries benefit most.</p>
<p><a href="https://whitespark.ca/local-search-ranking-factors/">Citation signals account for 7-13% of local pack ranking factors</a>, according to Whitespark's 2026 Local Search Ranking Factors survey. That percentage is smaller than it used to be. But citations still form the foundation of local SEO. Without them, Google cannot verify your business exists.</p>
<p>Here is what you will learn:</p>
<ul>
<li>The 100+ most impactful local citation sites ranked by priority</li>
<li>Which directories give dofollow backlinks vs nofollow</li>
<li>How data aggregators distribute your business info across 100+ platforms</li>
<li>Which industry-specific directories matter for your vertical</li>
<li>How local listings affect AI search visibility in ChatGPT and Perplexity</li>
</ul>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="Top local business listing sites ranked by domain authority and SEO impact" src="/images/blog/local-listing-sites-by-category.webp" /></p>
<h2>The 25 Best Local Business Listing Sites</h2>
<p><strong>1. <a href="https://business.google.com">Google Business Profile</a>. The Foundation</strong></p>
<p>Google Business Profile is the single most important local business listing site. Full stop. <a href="https://whitespark.ca/local-search-ranking-factors/">GBP signals account for about 32% of local pack ranking factors</a>. No other directory comes close to that influence.</p>
<p>A complete GBP listing gets <a href="https://www.brightlocal.com/resources/local-seo-statistics/">7x more clicks</a> than an incomplete one. Businesses in the Google 3-pack receive 126% more traffic and 93% more actions than those below it. Every field matters: business name, address, phone, hours, categories, photos, services, and products.</p>
<p>If you do nothing else from this list, <a href="/blog/optimize-google-business-profile/">optimize your Google Business Profile</a> completely. Everything else builds on this foundation.</p>
