<p><strong>2. <a href="https://businessconnect.apple.com">Apple Business Connect</a>. Powers Siri and Apple Maps</strong></p>
<p>Apple Business Connect is the second most important <a href="/glossary/local-seo/">local business listing</a> you can create. It powers Apple Maps, Siri voice search results, and business cards in the iPhone wallet. Apple devices account for roughly 55% of US mobile traffic.</p>
<p>The DA is 99. Listings are free. Apple Business Connect launched as a full dashboard in 2024, giving business owners direct control over photos, offers, and action buttons. Most competitors still have not claimed their Apple listing. That gap is your advantage.</p>
<p><strong>3. <a href="https://www.yelp.com">Yelp</a>. DA 93, Still a Ranking Factor</strong></p>
<p>Yelp has a DA of 93 and remains one of Google's most trusted review sources. <a href="https://www.brightlocal.com/resources/local-seo-statistics/">31% of top 10 organic results</a> for local searches are business directories. Yelp pages dominate that share.</p>
<p>Free listings include your business name, address, phone, hours, photos, and a link to your website. Links are nofollow. The real SEO value comes from Yelp pages ranking in Google for "[business type] near me" queries. A strong Yelp profile also feeds data to voice assistants and AI search engines. Restaurants, home services, and retail businesses benefit most from <a href="/blog/yelp-for-business/">Yelp optimization</a>.</p>
<p><strong>4. <a href="https://www.bingplaces.com">Bing Places</a>. Imports from GBP</strong></p>
<p>Bing Places has a DA of 94 and powers search results across Bing, Yahoo, and Microsoft Edge. Bing holds about 9% of US search market share. More importantly, Bing data feeds into Microsoft Copilot's AI search results.</p>
<p>The easiest setup: import your GBP listing directly into Bing Places. The platform copies your business name, address, phone, categories, and hours in one click. Free listing. NoFollow links. Takes under 5 minutes. If you have already <a href="/blog/optimize-google-business-profile/">optimized your GBP</a>, Bing Places is an instant win.</p>
<p><strong>5. <a href="https://www.facebook.com/business">Facebook Business Page</a>. DA 96</strong></p>
<p>Facebook has a DA of 96 and 3 billion monthly active users. Your Facebook Business Page serves as both a social profile and a local business listing. Google indexes Facebook Business Pages and often surfaces them in branded searches.</p>
<p>Links are nofollow. The value extends beyond SEO. Facebook reviews influence consumer trust. Your business page appears in Facebook's local search features. <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/local-seo-statistics/">62% of consumers</a> avoid businesses with incorrect information online. Keeping your Facebook NAP (name, address, phone) consistent with your GBP listing is critical for <a href="/blog/nap-consistency/">NAP consistency</a>.</p>
