<p><strong>12. <a href="https://www.angi.com">Angi (Angie's List)</a>. DA 78, Home Services</strong></p>
<p>Angi has a DA of 78 and dominates the home services directory space. Plumbers, electricians, HVAC technicians, roofers, and contractors get the most value from an Angi listing.</p>
<p>Free profiles are available. Links are nofollow. Angi's lead generation model means your listing appears when homeowners search for specific services in your area. Angi pages rank well in Google for "[service] near me" queries. If you run a <a href="/blog/home-services-seo-guide/">home services business</a>, Angi belongs in your top 10 citations.</p>
<p><strong>13. <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.com">TripAdvisor</a>. DA 93, Hospitality Essential</strong></p>
<p>TripAdvisor has a DA of 93 and dominates the travel and hospitality search results. Restaurants, hotels, tour operators, and entertainment venues need a TripAdvisor listing.</p>
<p>Free listings include photos, menus, hours, and a website link. Links are nofollow. TripAdvisor pages rank on page 1 of Google for thousands of "[restaurant] + [city]" and "[hotel] + [city]" queries. The platform also feeds data to AI search engines. If your business serves tourists or diners, TripAdvisor is a top-3 priority after GBP and Yelp.</p>
<p><strong>14. <a href="https://www.healthgrades.com">Healthgrades</a>. DA 88, Healthcare</strong></p>
<p>Healthgrades has a DA of 88 and is the leading directory for doctors, dentists, hospitals, and healthcare providers. The platform connects patients with providers based on location, specialty, and insurance.</p>
<p>Free provider profiles include your practice address, specialties, education, and hospital affiliations. Healthgrades pages rank for "[specialty] + [city]" queries in Google. For medical professionals running a <a href="/blog/dental-seo-guide/">dental practice</a> or healthcare office, Healthgrades often generates more patient inquiries than any other directory besides Google.</p>
<p><strong>15. <a href="https://www.avvo.com">Avvo</a>. DA 80, Legal</strong></p>
<p>Avvo has a DA of 80 and specializes in lawyer directories. The platform lets potential clients search for attorneys by practice area, location, and rating.</p>
<p>Free profiles include a dofollow backlink. That combination of high DA and dofollow links makes Avvo one of the most valuable industry-specific citations for <a href="/blog/law-firm-seo-guide/">law firms</a>. Avvo profiles rank well in Google for "[practice area] lawyer + [city]" queries. Complete your profile with client reviews, published articles, and a professional photo.</p>
<p><strong>16. <a href="https://www.houzz.com">Houzz</a>. DA 88, Home Design</strong></p>
<p>Houzz has a DA of 88 and connects homeowners with interior designers, architects, contractors, and home improvement professionals. The platform hosts 65 million+ monthly users.</p>
<p>Free profiles include project photos, reviews, and a website link. Houzz pages rank in Google Image search for home design queries. The visual portfolio format makes Houzz especially valuable for businesses that showcase their work through photos. Interior designers, kitchen remodelers, and landscape architects benefit most.</p>
<p><strong>17. <a href="https://www.zillow.com">Zillow</a>. DA 92, Real Estate</strong></p>
<p>Zillow has a DA of 92 and dominates real estate search. Agents, brokers, and property managers can create free profiles that include listings, reviews, and a website link.</p>
<p>Zillow agent profiles rank in Google for "[realtor] + [city]" queries. The platform attracts 230 million+ monthly visitors. For <a href="/blog/real-estate-seo-guide/">real estate professionals</a>, a Zillow profile is as important as a GBP listing. Complete profiles with active listings and client reviews outperform blank profiles significantly.</p>
